{"tid":1011350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半唔肯嚟拜年","createTime":"2019-02-06T17:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T19:18:23.000Z","uid":138670,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c20c21da9ab5b05f609659370b32f2aca57d74ac","tid":1011350,"uid":138670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:02:23.000Z","msg":"事源係佢話過嚟拜年先嘅<br />\n咁我第一次肯帶男朋友嚟拜年 係因為我重視佢<br />\n視佢為結婚對象 係時候要見下屋企人<br />\n<br />\n當我講起自己屋企人嘅性格佢突然話唔嚟<br />\n我知佢唔中意人地問3問4 但我屋企比較傳統 所以都會問下<br />\n佢仲話唔中意曬錢買嘢拜年 但我覺得冇咩禮貌 所以一定買下<br />\n點知佢發我爛炸話唔嚟 唔中意對住一班人<br />\n我真係呆撚左 覺得佢完全唔夠大方<br />\n我仲同埋屋企人講帶男朋友嚟 佢地仲有啲開心<br />\n<br />\n嬲嬲地鬧左佢一句過唔到世 以後搵第二個帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知點收科了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0044e2af01f56b7b24c768f4a7e74a884696fbd7","tid":1011350,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:03:41.000Z","msg":"過幾日屌返佢屎眼罰下佢囉你"},{"pid":"ef4cb0a341e83793a5c98c6275d457b1b95ba595","tid":1011350,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"冇另一半"},{"pid":"7bf014088e8bf3df3deb5641cd3162e5357d4fd3","tid":1011350,"uid":30578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"同性香港結唔到婚住"},{"pid":"a7837469a2c1f735e88162dbdd4adc7415192637","tid":1011350,"uid":138670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bf014088e8bf3df3deb5641cd3162e5357d4fd3","tid":1011350,"uid":30578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"同性香港結唔到婚住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"藍絲 認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824a9dfb886e79d61f825feead1082538e54b88b","tid":1011350,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"搵我"},{"pid":"d67a771d1ad6e3f18b75267332926a4f3349c9ed","tid":1011350,"uid":234321,"like":0,"dis